item.title: Runette - Your Sucess Is Our Goal
item.dc:creator: @DJxDARIENx DJxDARIENx
item.description:
@DJxDARIENx wrote:

[quote=“Loveandpower, post:8, topic:452437”][quote author=Soulcist link=topic=555316.msg4066369#msg4066369 date=1343927739]
Those forums and the homepage is ACTUALLY decent, otherwise I’m not sure about the server because of it being a PI.
[/quote]Not ALL PI’s are bad :s

I sort of like the forums but eh[/quote]

Soulcist:

Those forums and the homepage is ACTUALLY decent, otherwise I’m not sure about the server because of it being a PI.

Thank you guys for saying you guys like the forums :). We are still working , and adding stuff onto the server. It is about 2 or 3 days old right now. Still some problems to be fixed, but most of them are working GREAT! We have working Gwd, Kbd, Kalphite (Both forms in cave) And aton of mini games! The community is good, small right now; but good. Try the server out for alittle longer and you guys might find yourself staying with us .
